'''Musab Fahd Al-Juwayr''' ({{langx|ar|مُصْعَب فَهْد الْجُوَيْر}}; born 20 June 2003) is a Saudi Arabian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Saudi Pro League]] club [[Al-Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]].<ref name="soccerwayM">{{cite web |title=MUSAB FAHZ ALJUWAYR |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/musab-fahz-aljuwayr/692624/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=مصعب الجوير – Musab Fahz Al-Juwayr |url=https://www.kooora.com/?player=137157}}</ref> Since 2023, he has also played for the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].

==Career==
Al-Juwayr started his career at the youth teams of [[Al Hilal SFC|Al-Hilal]]. He was promoted to the first team during the 2021 summer training camp.<ref>{{cite web |title=جارديم يبدأ قيادة الهلال وعينه على الشبان|url=https://makkahnewspaper.com/article/1541659/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%A8/%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%8A%D9%85-%D9%8A%D8%A8%D8%AF%D8%A3-%D9%82%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%87%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%88%D8%B9%D9%8A%D9%86%D9%87-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%86}}</ref> He signed his first professional contract with the club on 8 August 2021.<ref>{{cite web |title=الهلال يوقّع مع "الجوير" حتى 2023.. ويظفر بخدمات خليفة الدوسري |url=https://sabq.org/QhgGyd}}</ref> He made his debut on 13 September 2021 in the [[AFC Champions League]] match against [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]].<ref>{{cite web |title=ESTEGHLAL VS. AL HILAL  0 – 2 |url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2021/09/13/asia/afc-champions-league/esteghlal/al-hilal-riyadh/3530076/}}</ref> Al-Juwayr made his league debut and scored his first goal for the club on 4 November in the 2–0 win against [[Damac FC|Damac]].<ref>{{cite web |title="الهلال" يقفز للمركز الثالث بثنائية في مرمى "ضمك"|url=https://akhbaar24.argaam.com/article/detail/572841/}}</ref> On 12 January 2024, Al-Juwayr renewed his contract with Al-Hilal before joining [[Al Shabab FC (Riyadh)|Al-Shabab]] on a six-month loan.<ref>{{cite web |title=الهلال يمدد عقد الجوير.. ويعيره إلى الشباب |url=https://arriyadiyah.com/829703}}</ref> On 1 September 2024, Al-Juwayr once again joined [[Al Shabab FC (Riyadh)|Al-Shabab]] on loan.<ref>{{cite web |title=الهلال يعلن إعارة مصعب الجوير إلى الشباب |url=https://slaati.com/2024/09/01/p2544090.html}}</ref>

On 3 August 2025, Al-Juwayr joined [[Al-Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]] on a five-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=رسميّا.. الجوير يرتدي قميص القادسية |url=https://arriyadiyah.com/871190}}</ref>

